{"tid":2144620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港海關: 金錢服務經營者應定期瀏覽美國財政部網站，以查閱最新資料","createTime":"2020-08-07T16:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T09:00:18.000Z","uid":5195,"like":103,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"54e7bd97fd4b477a5b283ec15c7fa5aa2b568def","tid":2144620,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:33:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.customs.gov.hk/filemanager/common/pdf/circular_UNSO_08082014_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.customs.gov.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Fcommon%2Fpdf%2Fcircular_UNSO_08082014_tc.pdf&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6GqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=673eb33a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.customs.gov.hk/filemanager/common/pdf/circular_UNSO_08082014_tc.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n(2) 美國總統行政命令第 13224 號<br />\n<br />\n繼香港海關在 2014 年 7 月 15 日發出相關通函後，現通知閣下，美國政府已更新根據行<br />\n政命令第 13224 號（&ldquo;行政命令&rdquo;）發出的指定個人及實體名單。最新資料可於美國財<br />\n政部網站<br />\n(<a href=\"http://www.treasury.gov/resource-center/sanctions/Programs/Documents/terror.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.treasury.gov%2Fresource-center%2Fsanctions%2FPrograms%2FDocuments%2Fterror.pdf&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6GqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=a3548e27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.treasury.gov/resource-center/sanctions/Programs/Documents/terror.pdf</a>）<br />\n內取覽。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">由於美國政府或會不時更新根依據行政命令發出的指定個人及實體的名單，金錢服務經<br />\n營者應定期瀏覽美國財政部的網站，以查閱最新資料。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n金錢服務經營者應查核其紀錄中有否出現上述名單內的姓名或名稱，並向聯合財富情報組報告其現時或過往與該等被指名人士或實體的任何交易或關係。"},{"pid":"d1ba176b88e2d6e3d2c7e1f7f01d4df2e0cf8c21","tid":2144620,"uid":335434,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:35:35.000Z","msg":"海關高層走得好前 幾年前已經諗定點應對老細俾美國制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257a5c21b1d01d2f228ffb5d039b64c33acf7228","tid":2144620,"uid":231594,"like":0,"di